flowchart LR
  %% Revia Stitch - Audit Flow (Report + Highlights)

  A["File Workspace<br/>(Viewer)"] -->|Click Audit| B["Audit Panel"]

  B --> C["Run Audit<br/>(manual trigger)"]
  C --> D["Audit Running<br/>Spinner + progress"]
  D --> E{Audit result}

  E -->|Success| R["Audit Report<br/>List of inconsistencies"]
  E -->|Failed| F["Audit Failed<br/>Retry + error details"]

  %% Report structure
  R --> R1["Each finding includes<br/>Type, Severity, Description"]
  R --> R2["Reference<br/>Page number + snippet"]
  R --> R3["Tags<br/>Terminology / attribute refs"]
  R --> R4["Actions<br/>Jump to highlight, Create change request"]

  %% Viewer integration
  R -->|Select finding| V["Viewer Jumps to Page<br/>Highlight bounding box"]
  V -->|Edit / comment| W["Collaborate<br/>Resolve / discuss"]
  V -->|Create fix| X["Edit Mode<br/>Apply changes"]
  X --> Y["Commit New Version<br/>(immutable)"]
  Y --> Z["Re-run Audit<br/>(optional)"]

